HEADWORD: Charon
<hw>Cha"ron</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr. Gr.
<?/.]</ety> <fld>(Cless. Myth.)</fld> <def>The son of Erebus and Nox,
